      Classes in bour.camus.gameofgooses.models.cells that implement ICell 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractCell
      AbstractCell represents a basic cell, and allows to avoid duplicating code.
      class  DepartureCell
      DepartureCell represents the first case of a Board.
      class  GooseCell
      GooseCell represents a cell allowing the Player to move again by the score of the die.
      class  NormalCell
      NormalCell represents a basic cell with absolutely no special effect.
      class  TeleportCell
      TeleportCell represents a cell where the Player is teleported to another cell upon arrival.
      class  TrapCell
      TrapCell represents a cell in which the Player is trapped, and can't play until someone replaces him in the case.
      class  WaitCell
      WaitCell represents a type of cell where the Player has to wait a specific amount of time before being able to play again.
